        "I compare simulation-only noise and hybrid hardware-informed noise. In the paper, I observe an average gain of about 6.5% F1 from hybrid noise training across architectures.\n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {},
